OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1780441387
OL,3,C'Distressing scene' for emergency
OL,4,Cteams trying to save teenager, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FAn inquest into the death of a teenage
OL,8,Fgirl, who died after being pulled from
OL,9,Fthe sea at Whitley Bay, has heard that
OL,10,Fit was a "very distressing scene" for
OL,11,Fthe emergency workers who treated her,
OL,12,Fbut that everyone was "doing their
OL,13,Fbest."
OL,15,FEdie Smart, 13, from Monkseaton, died
OL,16,Fon 28 July 2025. She had been in
OL,17,Fhospital, after being swept into the
OL,18,Fsea by a strong wave four days earlier.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1780441387
OL,3,C'Distressing scene' for emergency
OL,4,Cteams trying to save teenager, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FHer family believe that "opportunities
OL,8,Fmay not have been taken" along the
OL,9,Fway, which could have made a
OL,10,Fdifference to the outcome.
OL,12,FThe inquest, which is being held at
OL,13,FNewcastle Coroner's Court, today
OL,14,F(Tuesday 2 June) focused on some of
OL,15,Fthe treatment she received at the
OL,16,Fshore.
OL,18,FAs part of this, it heard from the
OL,19,Ffirst ambulance crew to arrive.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1780441387
OL,3,C'Distressing scene' for emergency
OL,4,Cteams trying to save teenager, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,F"It was a very distressing scene" said
OL,8,FCarl Patterson, an ambulance support
OL,9,Fpractitioner from the North East
OL,10,FAmbulance Service (NEAS), "But
OL,11,Feveryone was doing their best to stay
OL,12,Fcalm under the circumstances. We
OL,13,Fworked together as a team."
OL,15,FThe inquest heard that the teenager
OL,16,Fwas unconscious and had a significant
OL,17,Famount of seawater in her lungs.
OL,26,@rD@[OUuD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1780441387
OL,3,C'Distressing scene' for emergency
OL,4,Cteams trying to save teenager, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FA NEAS paramedic who also treated
OL,8,FEdie, Thomas Mortillaro, spoke about
OL,9,Fsome of the other difficulties they
OL,10,Ffaced.
OL,12,F"Edie was very small and that makes it
OL,13,Fchallenging... She was at floor level
OL,14,Fon a beach, which was sandy. The
OL,15,Fweather was bright which makes it
OL,16,Freally, really hard to see."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1780441387
OL,3,C'Distressing scene' for emergency
OL,4,Cteams trying to save teenager, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe inquest also heard that the first
OL,8,Fambulance crew to arrive (two
OL,9,Fambulance support practitioners) did
OL,10,Fnot have the authority to use the most
OL,11,Fpowerful type of suction machine
OL,12,Fneeded to help clear Edie's airways.
OL,14,F"It is not in our scope of practice to
OL,15,Fuse," said one, unless under the
OL,16,Fsupervision of a paramedic. They did
OL,17,Fuse a manual one.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1780441387
OL,3,C'Distressing scene' for emergency
OL,4,Cteams trying to save teenager, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe first paramedic on scene, who was
OL,8,Ffrom a third-party company, initially
OL,9,Fpresumed the two other ambulance staff
OL,10,Fthere were paramedics when they
OL,11,Fweren't. But said he was informed
OL,12,F"swiftly" and "took over straight
OL,13,Faway," noting that "everyone was doing
OL,14,Fan excellent job."
OL,16,FThe inquest also heard from Dr Rachel
OL,17,FAgbeko, a consultant at The Great
OL,18,FNorth Children's Hospital in Newcastle.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1780441387
OL,3,C'Distressing scene' for emergency
OL,4,Cteams trying to save teenager, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FShe and her team treated Edie, whose
OL,8,Fultimate cause of death was oxygen
OL,9,Fstarvation, cardiac arrest and
OL,10,Fdrowning.
OL,12,FThrough their lawyer, the family
OL,13,Fpassed on their thanks to all the
OL,14,Femergency services - and hospital -
OL,15,Fstaff who'd tried to save their
OL,16,Fdaughter.
OL,18,FThe inquest continues.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
